  "response": "A common term for pet lovers, especially those who love dogs, is \"canine enthusiast\" or \"dog lover.\" Additionally, you might come across the term \"dog parent,\" which reflects the affectionate bond many people have with their dogs. For a more whimsical touch, some people refer to themselves as \"dog owners\" or simply \"dog people.\" If you're looking for a specific title or name, \"dog aficionado\" could also work.",
